snippet.title: Amazing Discoveries In Outer Space - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Available for PS4: 2nd February US / 3rd February Europe
More info: http://www.adiosgame.com/

Amazing Discoveries In Outer Space (ADIOS) is an odyssey through the galaxy where physics-based space-flight and platforming action blend seamlessly together.

Explore a colorful universe filled with amazing discoveries, alien races, and fashionable hats.
